headline: Block Expands Merchant Reach With Dublin Hub And 7 Leaves Cafe Deal
summary: Block (NYSE:XYZ) opened a new office and demonstration lab in Dublin to support its European operations. Square, a Block business, entered into a partnership with 7 Leaves Cafe to support the chain’s nationwide U.S. operations. Block, through its Square ecosystem and other services, is active across merchant payments, point of sale software, and broader financial tools for businesses and individuals.
